title: EP 263: Andrew Horowitz: Can We Rally From Here?
itunes:title: Andrew Horowitz: Can We Rally From Here?
description:
This week, Andrew Horowitz, Host of The Disciplined Investor, joins Frank Curzio on Wall Street Unplugged to comment on the markets, breakdown recent earnings and how to short stocks.
 
    
Plus, Frank breaks down some of stocks he’s currently interested in and gives you his best ideas.
